name: Hyundai Kona
description: The Kona is an appealing pick among subcompact SUVs thanks to a strong optional turbocharged engine, sharp handling, and lots of features for the money. Hyundai's powertrain updates have further improved the driving experience, though it still has some drivability issues. A few shortcomings keep it from being an easy winner, such as a smaller-than-average cargo capacity and a plasticky cabin.

name: Tata Indica
description: The Indica is a compact SUV with a 4-cylinder engine and a 4-door configuration. It has a 5-speed manual transmission and a 5-speed automatic transmission.

name: Hyundai Elantra
description: The Elantra is a compact SUV with a 4-cylinder engine and a 4-door configuration. It has a 5-speed manual transmission and a 5-speed automatic transmission. The Elantra is available in two trim levels: the base model and the Sport.

name: Toyota Corolla
description: The Corolla is a off-road vehicle with a 4-cylinder engine and a 4-door configuration. It has a general-purpose 5-speed manual transmission and a 5-speed automatic transmission. The Corolla is available in two trim levels: the base model and the Sport. The base model has a 1.6-liter engine with a 5-speed manual transmission.

name: Chevrolet Impala
description: A spacious and comfortable sedan, ideal for long drives and known for its smooth ride.

name: Nissan Altima
description: A midsize sedan blending performance and efficiency, perfect for families and commuters.

name: BMW 3 Series
description: A luxury sedan combining elegance, comfort, and cutting-edge technology.
